data.description: This gorgeous custom built craftsman style home is better than new and what a beauty it is! Located within the highly desired Pendleton School district and within a two minute drive to Portman Marina for lake lovers! Save $$$$ by being outside the city limits and enjoy the freedom of no HOA. When you tour the home you will love the attention to detail and upgrades. A covered front porch is the perfect spot to greet your guests. Entry is to the large and welcoming living room which is open to the breakfast area and fantastic kitchen. The kitchen offers granite countertops and gleaming white cabinetry, a large island counter to prep your meals and a full stainless large appliance package including an upgraded refrigerator which passes with the sale. Park your cars in the 2 car enclosed garage and enter through the mud room with cabinets and boot seating. Store groceries in the large walk in pantry. Your laundry room is designed to provide storage and have plenty of room. Your master suite has tray ceilings and a walk in closet along with an upgraded tiled walk in shower with glassed shower door.  The master bath is very beautiful and inviting! Two lovely guest rooms share a full bath with a shower/tub combination. Enjoy 2" blinds throughout most of the home. Pet lovers will greatly benefit from the expansive wooden privacy fence installed by the seller.  The yard has lots of space for pets and or children to play. You just can't beat this location. The floor plan is one of the best I've ever seen in this size home.
